{"tid":1533703,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"將一世都唔會原諒黑警做世世代代既家規","createTime":"2019-09-02T19:35:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T19:53:48.000Z","uid":163988,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"25b1c6ec8940848a41194968a3f800d1401a0bed","tid":1533703,"uid":163988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T19:35:10.000Z","msg":"從來都未試過憎一樣野/物種咁耐<br />\n但黑警 令我做到了<br />\n香港人 應承我<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">世世代代都唔可以原諒黑警<br />\n世世代代子孫都要視警察做最低賤既職業</span></span></strong><br />\n由細到大都要教育下一代（如果有）<br />\n香港警察=過街老鼠<br />\n等歷史記住香港警察既惡行<br />\n講到連佢地都懷疑人生<br />\n三個月啦 <br />\n仲係冇一個警隊既人有出黎表態<br />\n唔好同我講咩文職/自己有自己信念<br />\n無一個係無辜！！<br />\n禍必及妻兒！！"},{"pid":"cc8d7edc4b6a130fd66c5159b9495c58000e0c8a","tid":1533703,"uid":218443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T19:38:10.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母死全家！"},{"pid":"a34f835d50e5c35360bdfa3c231d3c77bc4e29c5","tid":1533703,"uid":285368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T19:38:55.000Z","msg":"612 721 831"},{"pid":"9ab033a741e028c22de49bfb319267ae472f504b","tid":1533703,"uid":98926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T19:53:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">8/9去美國領事館請願</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">派人道支援/過人權法</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G3i9E9a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG3i9E9a.png&h=b678595e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M80cCFS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM80cCFS.png&h=5da9f118&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另有大量文宣推<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>人權法</strong></span><br />\n<strong>請瘋狂tweet and retweet</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.g